    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"张小伦的网络日志","description":"欢迎来到张小伦的网络日志 \n\t\t一个记录生活，分享心得的博客","menu":[{"id":"home","name":"首页","url":"/"},{"id":"category","name":"分类","url":"/categories"},{"id":"archive","name":"归档","url":"/archives"},{"id":"about","name":"关于我","url":"/about"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"5ec4ea4b-3583-5231-a8c6-2ebc6dc1b28d","html":"<p>###pip的安装</p>\n<p>先下载一个 python 文件 : <a href=\"https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py\">get-pip.py</a>。\r\n然后运行下面这条命令（可能需要管理员权限）：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">python get-pip.py</code></pre></div>\n<p>如果 <a href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/setuptools\">setuptools</a> 还没有安装，pip会帮你安装。如果想更新已经存在的 setuptools，只要运行</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">pip install -U setuptools</code></pre></div>\n<p>为了确保能够在命令行中使用 <code>pip</code> 命令，确保将 Python 安装目录中的 <code>Scripts</code> 文件夹路径添加到系统的环境变量中。这个必须手动添加！</p>\n<p>###升级 pip</p>\n<p>在 Linux 或者 Mac 中：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">pip install -U pip</code></pre></div>\n<p>在 Window 中：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">python -m pip install -U pip</code></pre></div>\n<p>###安装 packages</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ pip install SomePackage            # latest version\r\n$ pip install SomePackage==1.0.4     # specific version\r\n$ pip install 'SomePackage>=1.0.4'     # minimum version</code></pre></div>\n<p>###卸载 packages</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">    $ pip install SomePackage</code></pre></div>\n<p>所以，在成功安装了 pip之后，可以使用 pip 安装 Django</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">pip install Django==1.6.5</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"利用pip安装Django","date":"July 12, 2014","description":null,"categories":["Python"],"tags":["Python"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blogs/git使用笔记(一)/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Git 使用笔记(一)-入门级的操作"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blogs/(译)取消事件冒泡的危害/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"(译)阻止事件传播的危害","draft":null,"tags":["译文","JavaScript"],"categories":[],"status":"publish"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"5ec4ea4b-3583-5231-a8c6-2ebc6dc1b28d","previousPostId":"58aa0b6a-c0c1-592f-9769-b07bf14534b2","nextPostId":"370c792e-099d-5e57-8328-93f05e976a63"}},
